# Privacy Policy for Banks Buddy

**Effective Date**: January 8, 2025

Banks Buddy ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting it through this Privacy Policy. This document explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application, Banks Buddy ("App"). Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your data.

## 1. Information We Collect

When you use Banks Buddy, we may collect the following types of information:

### a. Personal Data
* **Bank Details**: Includes account numbers, IBAN numbers, and other details you save in the App. This data is stored locally on your device and is not uploaded to our servers.

### b. Device Information
* Information about your device, including your device model, operating system, app version, and unique device identifiers.

### c. Usage Data
* Information on how you interact with the App, including features you use, app performance, and other analytical data.

### d. Advertising Data
* Information collected by Google AdMob for personalized and non-personalized ads.

## 2. How We Use Your Information

The information collected is used to:
* Allow you to save, manage, and share your bank details conveniently.
* Provide app functionalities such as copying or sharing details (complete or partial) via WhatsApp or other platforms.
* Improve the performance and functionality of the App.
* Show personalized and non-personalized advertisements via Google AdMob.
* (In future versions) Offer in-app purchases to enhance your experience.

## 3. Data Storage and Security

* **Local Storage**: All bank details you save are stored locally on your device. We do not access, collect, or store your sensitive bank details on any external servers or databases.
* **Security Measures**: We implement standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, please note that no system can guarantee complete security.

## 4. Sharing Your Information

Banks Buddy does not share your personal information with any third parties except in the following cases:
* **When You Choose to Share**: Bank details can be shared via WhatsApp or other platforms as per your instructions.
* **Advertising Partners**: Google AdMob may collect data to display ads within the App. For more information, review Google AdMob's Privacy Policy.

## 5. Third-Party Services

The App may include third-party services such as:
* **Google AdMob**: For advertisements.
* **WhatsApp and Other Platforms**: For sharing bank details directly.

These third-party services operate under their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review their policies for more information on their practices.

## 6. Children's Privacy

Banks Buddy is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children.

## 7. Future Features and Updates

We may add new features, including in-app purchases, in future versions of the App. This Privacy Policy will be updated accordingly to reflect changes.

## 8. Your Rights

You have the right to:
* Manage or delete your bank details saved within the App.
* Opt-out of personalized advertisements (as permitted by Google AdMob).
* Contact us regarding any concerns about your privacy.

## 9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted within the App with a new effective date.

## 10. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:
